SUMMARY:Easter Celebration
DESCRIPTION:Please plan to join MUCC on Sunday\, April 5th as we celebrate Easter. This will be a joyous celebration with plenty of music and gift bags for the kids and ending with a rousing rendition of the Hallelujah Chorus! The MUCC Children’s Gathering Space will also be open on this Sunday from 9:30 to 11:30 for all kiddos ages 0-5 of families who are attending Worship Services. After Worship\, all of the young and young at heart are invited to the Easter Egg hunt outside and all are invited up to Pilgrim Hall for Fellowship with Mimosas and Hot Cross buns. Invite your family\, friends\, and neighbors to this joyous celebration of hope!
URL:https://discovermagnolia.org/event/easter-celebration/
LOCATION:Magnolia United Church of Christ\, 3555 W McGraw St\, Seattle\, WA\, 98199\, United States
CATEGORIES:Holiday observance
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://discovermagnolia.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/Easter-for-popup-002.png
END:VEVENT
