LAST-MODIFIED:20260320T143748Z
UID:10001282-1777111200-1777122000@discovermagnolia.org
SUMMARY:Just Shred It!
DESCRIPTION:April 25\, 2026; Just Shred IT! 10 AM to 1 PM\, KeyBank parking lot\, W. McGraw St and 34th Ave W. \nEnter off W. McGraw St.     All Residences and Businesses are invited to bring their important papers \nto be commercially shredded. Save time and effort while gaining peace of mind that your important papers and information are disposed of in a safe and professional manner.  Old tax records\, old files\, save time and effort.  A $10 donation per box/bag is suggested.  Donations benefit our 501 (c) (3) Rotary Club of Magnolia Charitable Foundation.  We will provide you a tax receipt. First come first served. \nQuestions\, please contact Bryce McWalter\, 206-283-2037 or info@magnoliarotary.org.
URL:https://discovermagnolia.org/event/just-shred-it-5/
LOCATION:Key Bank\, 2401 34th Ave W\, Seattle\, WA\, 98199\, United States
CATEGORIES:fund raiser,Public Service
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://discovermagnolia.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/Just-Shred-It.jpg
ORGANIZER;CN="Rotary Club of Magnolia":MAILTO:info@magnoliarotary.org
END:VEVENT
