SUMMARY:Parents Night Out
DESCRIPTION:Bilingual Beginnings Preschool is hosting Parents Night Out during Vino in the Village. While you enjoy the event\, your child will have a fun evening with Spanish-themed activities\, arts & crafts\, and games. Dinner and snacks are included.
URL:https://discovermagnolia.org/event/parents-night-out/
LOCATION:Bilingual Beginnings\, 3320 W McGraw St\, Seattle\, WA\, 98199\, United States
CATEGORIES:Kids
