SUMMARY:Pet First Aid
DESCRIPTION:Join us for a day of the most comprehensive pet first aid course available! Our Walks ‘n’ Wags certified instructors offer a day of fun and learning. Classes are intended for pet care professionals\, dog and cat owners\, rescue workers\, first responders\, groomers and shelter workers. Course completion offers continuing education credits for PSI\, IAABC\, IACP and CBCC-KA members. This class has received the Animal Wellness Magazine Stamp of Approval and a Modern Dog Fave Find. We work with live animals in class.
URL:https://discovermagnolia.org/event/pet-first-aid/2026-05-02/
LOCATION:Metro Dog\, 4020 23rd Ave W\, Seattle\, WA\, 98119\, United States
CATEGORIES:Education,Health,Pets
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://discovermagnolia.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/pet-first-aid-metrodog.jpg
END:VEVENT
