DESCRIPTION:Discover a curated mix of vintage finds\, local makers\, handmade goods\, sweet treats\, coffee\, and food—plus a vintage warehouse full of gems to explore. \nWhether you’re hunting for one-of-a-kind pieces or just enjoying the Magnolia neighborhood\, this is your weekend spot. Bring a friend\, bring your pup\, and come hang out.
URL:https://discovermagnolia.org/event/magnolia-flea-market-2/2026-08-08/
